I had to think
something through.

1086
00:50:26.901 --> 00:50:28.403
There's... there's
a trust I manage.

1087
00:50:28.486 --> 00:50:30.072
Let's use the funds
from there to replenish

1088
00:50:30.155 --> 00:50:31.573
the Philips account.

1089
00:50:31.656 --> 00:50:33.533
<i>Sure.</i>

1090
00:50:33.616 --> 00:50:35.827
